  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nToday `forge fmt` automatically \"cuddles\" elses:\r\n```solidity\r\nif (true) {\r\n  // ...\r\n} else {\r\n  // ...\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI could not find a way to change this.\r\n\r\nWhile this is a common format there are two other common formats:\r\n```solidity\r\nif (true) {\r\n  // ...\r\n}\r\nelse {\r\n  // ...\r\n}\r\n```\r\n```solidity\r\nif (true)\r\n{\r\n  // ...\r\n}\r\nelse\r\n{\r\n  // ...\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nCould we maybe add a new `fmt` option, e.g. `if_braces_style` ?\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
